OL,5, A midwife with long Covid has said she 
OL,6, feels "abandoned and angry".           
OL,8,FNew NHS sickness absence rules mean    
OL,9,FSarah Sutton, 44, from Swansea, will   
OL,10,Fnot be paid after 1 November unless she
OL,11,Fis able to return to work.             
OL,13,FShe contracted the virus in 2020 while 
OL,14,Fworking as a community midwife at Neath
OL,15,FPort Talbot Hospital.                  
OL,17,FThe Welsh government said NHS Wales and
OL,18,Ftrade unions agreed the new Covid      
OL,19,Fsickness absence rules, which began on 
OL,20,F1 July.                                
